Package: PaperPlotR
Title: Publication-Ready ggplot2 Helpers for Scientific Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Qingguo", "Zeng", email = "228021575+Qgzeng-Bio@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A companion package for scientific figure workflows built on
    top of 'ggplot2'. It provides reusable themes, figure-size presets,
    semantic color helpers, multi-panel layout tools, export helpers, and
    lightweight wrappers for common comparison plots used in manuscripts
    and reports.
URL: https://github.com/Qgzeng-Bio/Paperplotr,
    https://qgzeng-bio.github.io/Paperplotr/
BugReports: https://github.com/Qgzeng-Bio/Paperplotr/issues
